      "x": -2900,
      "y": -323,
      "name": "authFlowNote",
      "width": 560,
      "height": 400,
      "content": "🔄 COMPLETE AUTH USER FLOWS\n\n── SIGN-UP JOURNEY ──\nsign-up\n  → modal-otp (email verification code overlay)\n  → onboarding-step1 (profile details: company name, role, team size)\n  → onboarding-step2 (preferences / goals)\n  → modal-allset ('You're all set!' confirmation overlay)\n  → redirect: Candidate → /test/sample/intro | Company → /dashboard\n\n── LOGIN JOURNEY ──\nlogin → /dashboard (Company) or /test/sample/intro (Candidate)\n\n── PASSWORD RESET JOURNEY ──\nforgot-password (enter email)\n  → otp-verify (enter reset code)\n  → new-password (set new password)\n  → login\n\n📌 AUTH-01: Role selector on sign-up drives redirect destination\n📌 AUTH-03: forgot-password is entry point; otp-verify + new-password are the continuation screens (not in original plan — added to design)"
    },
