      "height": 519,
      "content": "⚠️ ERROR STATE FRAMES — STILL NEEDED\n\nThe plan requires separate frames for form error states:\n• sign-up--error\n  Red borders on email + password fields\n  Inline errors: 'Please enter a valid email address' / 'Password must be at least 8 characters'\n  CTA at 50% opacity (disabled)\n\n• login--error\n  Red border on email/password field\n  Inline error: 'Invalid email or password'\n  CTA at 50% opacity (disabled)\n\nCurrently only annotated via lErrNote (x:4562). Create these as full separate frames before Phase 4 begins so implementers have a visual reference for the error state layout."
    }
